# ─── Supabase ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Your Project → Settings → API
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ─── Optional: Real Embeddings ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# To use real embeddings instead of the mock, implement generateEmbedding()
# in utils/embeddings.ts. Options:
#
# 1. Ollama (nomic-embed-text — free, local):
#    Pull the model: ollama pull nomic-embed-text
#    Then update utils/embeddings.ts (see the comment in that file)
#
# 2. OpenAI text-embedding-3-small:
#    OPENAI_API_KEY=...
#
# 3. Cohere embed-english-v3.0:
#    COHERE_API_KEY=...
